=== spellbook of force bolt ===
qty=1 identified buc=blessed -> a blessed spellbook of force bolt
qty=1 identified buc=uncursed -> an uncursed spellbook of force bolt
qty=1 identified buc=cursed -> a cursed spellbook of force bolt
qty=1 identified buc=buc_unknown -> a spellbook of force bolt
qty=1 unidentified -> a vellum spellbook
qty=1 called=attack? -> a spellbook called attack?
qty=3 identified buc=blessed -> 3 blessed spellbook of force bolts
qty=3 identified buc=uncursed -> 3 uncursed spellbook of force bolts
qty=3 identified buc=cursed -> 3 cursed spellbook of force bolts
qty=3 identified buc=buc_unknown -> 3 spellbook of force bolts
qty=3 unidentified -> 3 vellum spellbooks
qty=3 called=attack? -> 3 spellbook called attack?s
=== spellbook of healing ===
qty=1 identified buc=blessed -> a blessed spellbook of healing
qty=1 identified buc=uncursed -> an uncursed spellbook of healing
qty=1 identified buc=cursed -> a cursed spellbook of healing
qty=1 identified buc=buc_unknown -> a spellbook of healing
qty=1 unidentified -> a parchment spellbook
qty=1 called=attack? -> a spellbook called attack?
qty=3 identified buc=blessed -> 3 blessed spellbook of healings
qty=3 identified buc=uncursed -> 3 uncursed spellbook of healings
qty=3 identified buc=cursed -> 3 cursed spellbook of healings
qty=3 identified buc=buc_unknown -> 3 spellbook of healings
qty=3 unidentified -> 3 parchment spellbooks
qty=3 called=attack? -> 3 spellbook called attack?s
